{"tid":2430666,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"指淺色衫中年男女自由出入閘  證人：白衣人針對黑衫青年","createTime":"2021-03-03T05:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T05:50:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2cd38871f9284c07fce29bcea1a553165542e3ce","tid":2430666,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:43:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/MLTL7DN5TFAJTF5LVJZ6AP467Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2FMLTL7DN5TFAJTF5LVJZ6AP467Y%2F&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiur9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=206be4fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2FMLTL7DN5TFAJTF5LVJZ6AP467Y%2F&h=2f888626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/MLTL7DN5TFAJTF5LVJZ6AP467Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n指淺色衫中年男女自由出入閘 <br />\n證人：白衣人針對黑衫青年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/M9JjjuYk6g5nnkD4835vW_HKs-E=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4MNYRDLGSVCTFLUSOQMXLWMACY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FM9JjjuYk6g5nnkD4835vW_HKs-E%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4MNYRDLGSVCTFLUSOQMXLWMACY.jpg&h=9ea69165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■證人D（穿黑衣者）當日在元朗站遭多個白衣人圍毆。<br />\n<br />\n【721元朗黑夜】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：片揭施襲者撤離後 車長即開車<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】7.21元朗站白衣人暴動及傷人案續審，辯方昨盤問目擊證人時聲言案發時其他市民能如常出入閘。證人同意，但強調當時能自由出入閘的多為穿白色或淺色衣物中年男女，白衣人展露敵意目標似乎針對黑衫年輕人；他自言未有思考白衣人當時的目標是否在場的林卓廷。雖然本案控罪聚焦在晚上10時後元朗站內事件，但有證人表示，當晚其實早至8時許，網上已流傳白衣人襲擊市民片段。<br />\n<br />\n除證人A接受辯方盤問，法庭昨先後傳。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不同意辯方指「牛屎佬」挑釁<br />\n<br />\nA日前供稱觀察到有白衣人手綁紅絲帶，疑擔任「雞頭」司令角色；謝昨指，不能排。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n謝播放片段，稱月台市民曾在樓梯位置、向下方淺色衫人士投擲金屬垃圾桶，造成。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當晚片段顯示市民一方有女子曾以粗言怒罵白衣人「牛屎佬」，謝質疑。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n第二名出庭的目擊證人D，聲線似年輕男子，他作供憶述當晚準備由輕鐵轉乘西鐵回家，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nD續供稱，看見閘外一名橙衣女子被一人追打，施襲者穿牛仔褲及粉紅色短袖上衣，手持棍或藤條。半分鐘後D也被打，四至六名穿白衣或淺色衫的人追住他頭部及身軀圍毆，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n控方隨後傳召第三名證人B，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n控方問及B所指的網上消息，B稱。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC888/19、11、734/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6RVtjQdienJEmskxaVCxX93I_Y0=/930x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FOO6AFH7PVELVKCNTP7NOGHZ2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6RVtjQdienJEmskxaVCxX93I_Y0%3D%2F930x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFOO6AFH7PVELVKCNTP7NOGHZ2Y.jpg&h=c9c49902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林卓廷當日遭數十名白衣人圍毆至嘴角流血。"},{"pid":"cf6887565af0d9aec1e186a29b9cc557e3ad4921","tid":2430666,"uid":121546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:45:14.000Z","msg":"又開始改寫歷史<br />\n班黑社會明明見人就打"},{"pid":"aeb0c63a996a44f4d1f2adf70b7441f6669a9600","tid":2430666,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:47:05.000Z","msg":"D續供稱，看見閘外一名橙衣女子被一人追打，<span class=\"pink\">施襲者穿牛仔褲及粉紅色短袖上衣，手持棍或藤條。</span>半分鐘後D也被打，四至六名穿白衣或淺色衫的人追住他頭部及身軀圍毆，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n應該得一條友著粉紅色衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb2a42c308a587b9e21ef77960e413952ab0c1e","tid":2430666,"uid":35774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aeb0c63a996a44f4d1f2adf70b7441f6669a9600","tid":2430666,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:47:05.000Z","msg":"D續供稱，看見閘外一名橙衣女子被一人追打，<span class=\"pink\">施襲者穿牛仔褲及粉紅色短袖上衣，手持棍或藤條。</span>半分鐘後D也被打，四至六名穿白衣或淺色衫的人追住他頭部及身軀圍毆，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n應該得一條友著粉紅色衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-0